+----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+----------------------------------------------------------------------

Playing RBDOOM-3-BFG requires the Steam or GOG copy of the game.

Copy all content of the original game to the appropriate
directories:

~/.local/share/rbdoom3bfg/

These direcotories will contain user data, such as game settings, 
log, and saves.

For more information, see:
https://github.com/RobertBeckebans/RBDOOM-3-BFG
